&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;img src="//localhost:1313/imgs/img-lazy-loading.gif" data-src="image-20211114141517710.png" alt="image-20211114141517710" />&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>证书相关</title><link>//localhost:1313/posts/tech-openssl/</link><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2019 15:23:10 +0000</pubDate><guid>//localhost:1313/posts/tech-openssl/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>来看看互联网世界的基石&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;h2 id="通信过程的简化模型">通信过程的简化模型
&lt;a class="header-anchor" href="#%e9%80%9a%e4%bf%a1%e8%bf%87%e7%a8%8b%e7%9a%84%e7%ae%80%e5%8c%96%e6%a8%a1%e5%9e%8b">&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;h3 id="第一阶段-服务器向ca发起证书签名请求">第一阶段: 服务器向CA发起证书签名请求
&lt;a class="header-anchor" href="#%e7%ac%ac%e4%b8%80%e9%98%b6%e6%ae%b5-%e6%9c%8d%e5%8a%a1%e5%99%a8%e5%90%91ca%e5%8f%91%e8%b5%b7%e8%af%81%e4%b9%a6%e7%ad%be%e5%90%8d%e8%af%b7%e6%b1%82">&lt;/a>
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>服务器组织生成一个私钥&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:2;-o-tab-size:2;tab-size:2;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>openssl genrsa -out target.key &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff">1024&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>从私钥文件中得到公钥, 这个公钥会被用于给CA签名&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:2;-o-tab-size:2;tab-size:2;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>openssl rsa -in target.key -pubout -out target_pub.key
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>使用私钥生成一个证书签名请求, 在生成过程中需要填写证书申请人的一些信息&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>使用hexo和github搭建网站</title><link>//localhost:1313/posts/tech-hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2019 03:12:31 +0000</pubDate><guid>//localhost:1313/posts/tech-hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="基础修改">基础修改
&lt;a class="header-anchor" href="#%e5%9f%ba%e7%a1%80%e4%bf%ae%e6%94%b9">&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>修改 _config.yml，写上网站的标题&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:2;-o-tab-size:2;tab-size:2;">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>title:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>subtitle:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>description:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>选择主题&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:2;-o-tab-size:2;tab-size:2;">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>theme: next
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="hexo-插件">hexo 插件
&lt;a class="header-anchor" href="#hexo-%e6%8f%92%e4%bb%b6">&lt;/a>
&lt;/h2>&lt;h3 id="字数统计和阅读时长统计">字数统计和阅读时长统计
&lt;a class="header-anchor" href="#%e5%ad%97%e6%95%b0%e7%bb%9f%e8%ae%a1%e5%92%8c%e9%98%85%e8%af%bb%e6%97%b6%e9%95%bf%e7%bb%9f%e8%ae%a1">&lt;/a>
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>
&lt;a href="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-symbols-count-time" title="https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-symbols-count-time" rel="noopener external nofollow noreferrer" target="_blank" class=" exturl">
 https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-symbols-count-time
 
 &lt;i class="fa fa-external-link-alt">&lt;/i>
 
&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>在 _config.yml 中添加&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:2;-o-tab-size:2;tab-size:2;">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>symbols_count_time:
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> symbols: true
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> time: true
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> total_symbols: true
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> total_time: true
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> exclude_codeblock: false
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> awl: 4
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> wpm: 275
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> suffix: &amp;#34;mins.&amp;#34;
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>在Next主题中的 _config.yml中添加&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>ch3n9w 的 vim</title><link>//localhost:1313/posts/tech-ch4ser-vim/</link><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2019 02:05:35 +0000</pubDate><guid>//localhost:1313/posts/tech-ch4ser-vim/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="ch3n9w-的-vim">ch3n9w 的 vim
&lt;a class="header-anchor" href="#ch3n9w-%e7%9a%84-vim">&lt;/a>
&lt;/h1>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>本篇文章中的插件均已过时, 不推荐使用&lt;/p>
&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>《程序员修炼之道》中有一句话:&lt;code>最好是精通一种编辑器，并将其用于所有编辑任务。如果不坚持使用一种编辑器，可能会面临现代的巴别特大混乱。&lt;/code> ，实质今日，深以为然。而自从接触vim之后我一直都保持着有空折腾折腾的好习惯，它的简洁和高度自由让人着迷，围绕着vim衍生出的插件数不胜数。奈何插件繁多的同时也意味着选择的困难和配置的繁琐。为了准备以后可能出现的突发情况比如配置丢失或者重新安装，特在此以实现特定功能为主题，记录自己配置vim的过程。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>